{"tid":26380,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得要尊重老師 難聽過粗口","createTime":"2016-12-06T16:19:40.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T20:28:26.000Z","uid":12529,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"00570ddcb159e8f8e3153c9b03c81e69ee9c0ea6","tid":26380,"uid":12529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T16:19:40.000Z","msg":"其實小學到中學<br />\nD老師都話 要尊重老師呀<br />\n做老師好辛苦架 番學要應付你地<br />\n番到屋企又要改簿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔係講全部<br />\n但我預見既十個有十個都係鳩佬黎<br />\n上堂hea教 得番拎電話出黎睇下股票<br />\n得閒又幫自己 老師呢個職業打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到5點就衝番屋企 <br />\n大佬呀 咩人先會grad左做老師<br />\n大部分都係讀唔到好d既科先會做老師<br />\n然後就串鳩你廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老師唔係聖人<br />\n老師只係一種職業<br />\n老師係well paid <br />\n年年加人工 又鐵飯碗<br />\n佢地有收錢架 <br />\n收左錢 唔該俾d責任心比d熱誠教書啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 岩聽俾個正皮"},{"pid":"4747ef4209f39a3959a42cf13c2b706aa1153f73","tid":26380,"uid":45914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T16:22:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99cf93914263c4c683a2daca7da5679f7682aaed","tid":26380,"uid":38832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T16:51:05.000Z","msg":"你錯啦 收咗錢就唔一定要俾熱誠你嘅<br />\n有熱誠教就唔俾錢都會教"},{"pid":"abda7640eefc7d083451304ae6c5f914fc9ae07b","tid":26380,"uid":36087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T16:51:59.000Z","msg":"唔係鐵飯碗"},{"pid":"a0a1d9afcdf74ce6b117b43172457ba7799c0921","tid":26380,"uid":12529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T17:06:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係鐵飯碗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔計呢幾年興起既contract制<br />\n知道呢幾年完左contract都係renew contract 唔轉你做perm<br />\n講緊係做緊perm果d 19佬"},{"pid":"a90079c56a887c60ffda4737f1fd4ab0aa6d5dea","tid":26380,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T17:15:55.000Z","msg":"古人講尊師重道，係